/*
=head1 Custom Operators
d9057 2
a9058 3
=for apidoc Ao||custom_op_xop
Return the XOP structure for a given custom op. This function should be
considered internal to OP_NAME and the other access macros: use them instead.
d9060 3
a9062 2
=cut
*/
